1 (1), 57–62.</cite> [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1093/bfgp/elr041" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOI</a>] [<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22210853/" class="usa-link">PubMed</a>] [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Genomics&amp;title=Differential%20expression-%20the%20next%20generation%20and%20beyond.%20Brief%20Funct&amp;author=PL%20Auer&amp;author=S%20Srivastava&amp;author=RW%20Doerge&amp;volume=1&amp;issue=1&amp;publication_year=2012&amp;pages=57-62&amp;pmid=22210853&amp;doi=10.1093/bfgp/elr041&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
